"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-05-adam-peaty-blasts-cheating-chinese-swimmers-olympics-its-fraud-21361347\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Adam Peatydid not hold back in criticising 'cheating' atParis2024, slamming previously 'contaminated' Chinese swimmers after the 4x100m medley.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 102, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.7665525176669575, \"rank\": 0.30045442928052135, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GBfinished fourth in the medley, withChinawinning gold, but Peaty was not happy seeing the team stand atop the podium.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two of the four-man team, Qin Haiyang and Sun Jiajun, were among 11 swimmers allowed to compete in Paris despite testing positive for a banned substance.\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"score\": 0.9999938624996128, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Qin Haiyang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\"}, {\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Media\", \"score\": 0.9651081987446113, \"rank\": 0.032409333555069586, \"text\": \"Sun\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Media\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jiajun\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jiajun\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jiajun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jiajun\"}, {\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999991778168, \"rank\": 8.221514097923328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were allowed to swim because the China Anti-Doping Agency decided the positive tests were down to food contamination.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Peaty is certainly not entirely accepting of that judgement, suggesting that the athletes who tested positive should not be in Paris.\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999991778168, \"rank\": 8.221514097923328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'One of my favourite quotes in sport is that there is no point winning if you are not winning fair,' said Peaty said.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think you know that in your heart.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you touch and you know you are cheating, then you are not really winning.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'So for me, if you have been \\\"contaminated\\\" twice, I think as an honourable person you should be out of the sport.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we know sport is not that simple.\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have got to have faith in the system, but we do not.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just got to be stricter.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What I have said from the start is that it is fraud.\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are cheating, it is fraud.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's not about the podium.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We did our best job as a team, it may have been bronze, who knows, shoulda woulda coulda, who knows?\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am glad I was able to come out of my illness this week and give my best and be fair.\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not need anything else to do that, just my heart, that's what sport is.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And for me, being a man of faith, we can not take any of this with us, but we can take our pride and we can take the memories we share with our families, knowing we did it true.'\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty made it clear that he wasn't referring to the entire Chinese team, or other athletes, saying: 'I have also been asked about people who were not contaminated and I respect that.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.7665525176669575, \"rank\": 0.30045442928052135, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want to paint a whole nation or a group of people with one brush.\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that would be very unfair.'\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 100m breaststroke silver medallist at this year's Gamesalso hit out at swimming chiefs, suggesting that they have not done their job properly.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking of Team GB's performance going forward, he said: 'I think we are going to use it to our advantage in the next four years, whether I am there or not.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know these boys will carry that and we will see how they do in four years' time.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But, the people that need to do their job, need to wake up and do it.'\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Xu Jiayu and Pan Zhanle completed the Chinese team, with Xu saying: 'There is no problem for the team.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2555, \"end\": 2563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xu_Jiayu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xu Jiayu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xu_Jiayu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xu_Jiayu\"}, {\"begin\": 2593, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.7665525176669575, \"rank\": 0.30045442928052135, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We follow the rules.\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not want to have any excuses.\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We overcame some challenges and just like in the past we won some battles, this is something that's rooted in the Chinese spirit.'\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2830, \"end\": 2837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.7665525176669575, \"rank\": 0.30045442928052135, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB silver medal downgraded to bronze on heartbreaking photo finish  ArrowMORE:Why one player wears a different colour in volleyball at the Olympics  ArrowMORE:Noah Lyles posts powerful message on mental and physical struggles after 100m gold  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 3338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2980, \"end\": 2987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999958751082922, \"rank\": 4.124891183444334e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 3144, \"end\": 3154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used